{"tid":794774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲文明處於「永嘉之亂」的前夜：穆斯林有目的性的人口置換","createTime":"2018-08-26T13:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T17:19:52.000Z","uid":62257,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f29a35904cb230d4cbb4925d7ed6be28d5657d","tid":794774,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yehi6ogd3nA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyehi6ogd3nA&d=5mV46kwijVc4JgWFdy%2BNoAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6fba30f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yehi6ogd3nA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XhmguFC2aIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXhmguFC2aIs&d=5mV46kwijVc4JgWFdy%2BNoAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b0e0dbd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XhmguFC2aIs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n永嘉之亂，或稱永嘉之禍，是發生在中國西晉時代永嘉五年（311年）的一場動亂事件。動亂由居於中原的外族人發動，外族軍隊擊敗西晉京師洛陽的守軍，攻陷洛陽並大肆搶掠殺戮，更俘擄晉懷帝等王公大臣。是中國歷史上第一次漢人政權治所被外族攻破後統治集團幾乎全滅的事件。及後西晉於316年滅亡。<br />\n<br />\n永嘉之亂後，晉朝統治集團南遷，定都建康（今南京）建立東晉，史稱衣冠南渡。"},{"pid":"339b181f3f1fe3e9dda28b321794c0a2596917c7","tid":794774,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"蠻族入侵，羅馬滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fc4bf6970362379d883bd04e133c1cd41ffb7f","tid":794774,"uid":81424,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"等任意一個歐洲國家非白人人口佔1/3嘅時候就係希特拉重臨之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f039637b2be430429ebbc658e7f18bfbab86f0f","tid":794774,"uid":53705,"like":28,"dislike":7,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"咁又唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n古代晉軍太